#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Com començar"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "When you start &kturtle; you will see something like this:"
msgstr "Quan inicieu el &kturtle; veureu quelcom com això:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &kturtle; when you start it for the first time"
msgstr ""
"Aquesta és una captura de pantalla del &kturtle; quan l'inicieu per primera "
"vegada"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kturtle; on a fresh start"
msgstr "El &kturtle; en un inici net"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this Getting Started guide we assume that the language of the "
"&turtlescript; commands is English. You can change this language with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Script Language</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu. Be aware that the language you set here "
"for &kturtle; is the one you use to type the &turtlescript; commands, not "
"the language used by &kde; on your computer and used to display the "
"&kturtle; interface and menus."
msgstr ""
"En aquesta guia sobre com començar assumirem que l'idioma de les ordres està "
"en anglès. Podeu canviar aquest idioma a l'element de menú "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Arranjament</guimenu><guimenuitem>Idioma de script</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Cal tenir en compte que l'idioma que heu "
"establert aquí per al &kturtle;, és el que utilitzareu per a escriure les "
"ordres de &turtlescript;, no l'idioma utilitzat pel &kde; al vostre "
"ordinador i ni l'utilitzat per a mostrar la interfície i els menús del "
"&kturtle;."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "First steps with &turtlescript;: meet the Turtle!"
msgstr "Els primers passos amb &turtlescript;: Trobar la Tortuga!"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must have noticed the turtle in the middle of the canvas: you are just "
"about to learn how to control it using commands in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Podeu haver observat la tortuga al centre del llenç: Esteu a punt d'aprendre "
"a controlar-la mitjançant les ordres a l'editor."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Turtle Moves"
msgstr "Els moviments de la tortuga"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let us start by getting the turtle moving. Our turtle can do 3 types of "
"moves, (1) it can move forwards and backwards, (2) it can turn left and "
"right and (3) it can go (jump) directly to a position on the screen. Try "
"this for example:"
msgstr ""
"Començarem per a aconseguir que la tortuga es mogui. La nostra tortuga pot "
"fer tres tipus de moviments, (1) pot desplaçar-se cap endavant i cap enrere, "
"(2) pot girar a l'esquerra i a la dreta i (3) pot anar (salt) directament a "
"una posició a la pantalla. Proveu això, per exemple:"

#. Tag: screen
#: getting-started.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 90"
msgstr ""
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 90"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type or copy-paste the code to the editor and execute it (using <link "
"linkend=\"run-execute\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice></link>) to see the result."
msgstr ""
"Escriviu-ho o copieu i enganxeu el codi a l'editor, i executeu-lo (emprant "
"<link linkend=\"run-execute\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Executa</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Executa</guimenuitem></menuchoice></link>) per a veure "
"el resultat."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you typed and executed the commands like above in the editor you might "
"have noticed one or more of the following things:"
msgstr ""
"Quan escriviu i executeu les ordres com abans a l'editor observareu una o "
"més de les següents coses:"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That &mdash; after executing the commands &mdash; the turtle moves up, draws "
"a line, and then turns a quarter turn to the left. This because you have "
"used the <link linkend=\"forward\"><userinput>forward</userinput></link> and "
"the <link linkend=\"turnleft\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link> "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"Que -després d'executar les ordres- la tortuga es mou cap amunt, dibuixa una "
"línia, i llavors gira un quart de volta cap a l'esquerra. Això és deu a què "
"heu utilitzat les ordres <link linkend=\"forward\"><userinput>forward</"
"userinput></link> i <link linkend=\"turnleft\"><userinput>turnleft</"
"userinput></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That the color of the code changed while you where typing it: this feature "
"is called <emphasis>intuitive highlighting</emphasis> &mdash; different "
"types of commands are highlighted differently. This makes reading large "
"blocks of code more easy."
msgstr ""
"Que el color del codi canvia a mesura que l'escriviu: Aquesta característica "
"s'anomena <emphasis>ressaltat intuïtiu</emphasis> -diferents tipus d'ordres "
"són ressaltades de manera diferent-. Això fa que la lectura de grans blocs "
"de codi sigui més fàcil."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "That the turtle draws a thin black line."
msgstr "La tortuga dibuixa una fina línia negra."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maybe you got an error message. This could simply mean two things: you could "
"have made a mistake while copying the commands, or you should still set the "
"correct language for the &turtlescript; commands (you can do that by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Script "
"Language</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu)."
msgstr ""
"Potser heu rebut un missatge d'error. Això simplement pot significar dues "
"coses: Que podríeu haver comès un error en copiar les ordres, o que encara "
"s'ha de definir l'idioma correcte per a les ordres de &turtlescript; (podeu "
"fer-ho amb el submenú <menuchoice><guimenu>Arranjament</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Idioma de script</guisubmenu></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will likely understand that <userinput>forward 100</userinput> "
"instructed the turtle to move forward leaving a line, and that "
"<userinput>turnleft 90</userinput> instructed the turtle to turn 90 "
"<glossterm linkend=\"degrees\">degrees</glossterm> to the left."
msgstr ""
"Vós interpreteu que en la instrucció <userinput>forward 100</userinput> la "
"tortuga s'ha de moure a partir d'una línia, i que la instrucció "
"<userinput>turnleft 90</userinput> serveix perquè la tortuga giri 90 "
"<glossterm linkend=\"degrees\">graus</glossterm> a l'esquerra."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please see the following links to the reference manual for a complete "
"explanation of the new commands: <link linkend=\"forward"
"\"><userinput>forward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"backward"
"\"><userinput>backward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"turnleft"
"\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link>, and <link linkend=\"turnright"
"\"><userinput>turnright</userinput></link>."
msgstr ""
"Fixeu-vos en els següents enllaços al manual de referència per a una "
"explicació més completa de les ordres: <link linkend=\"forward"
"\"><userinput>forward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"backward"
"\"><userinput>backward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"turnleft"
"\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link> i <link linkend=\"turnright"
"\"><userinput>turnright</userinput></link>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "More examples"
msgstr "Més exemples"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first example was very simple, so let us go on!"
msgstr "El primer exemple és molt senzill, el podeu fer sense cap dificultat!"

#. Tag: screen
#: getting-started.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"reset\n"
"\n"
"canvassize 200,200\n"
"canvascolor 0,0,0\n"
"pencolor 255,0,0\n"
"penwidth 5\n"
"\n"
"go 20,20\n"
"direction 135\n"
"\n"
"forward 200\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 141\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 45\n"
"\n"
"go 40,100"
msgstr ""
"reset\n"
"\n"
"canvassize 200,200\n"
"canvascolor 0,0,0\n"
"pencolor 255,0,0\n"
"penwidth 5\n"
"\n"
"go 20,20\n"
"direction 135\n"
"\n"
"forward 200\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 141\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 45\n"
"\n"
"go 40,100"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Again you can type or copy-paste the code to the editor or open the "
"<filename>arrow</filename> example in the <guimenu>Examples</guimenu> "
"submenu and execute it (using <link linkend=\"run-execute"
"\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice></link>) to see the result. In the next examples you are expected "
"to know the drill."
msgstr ""
"Altra vegada ho podeu escriure o copiar i enganxar a l'editor o obrir "
"l'exemple <filename>arrow</filename> que trobareu en el submenú "
"<guimenu>Exemples</guimenu> i executeu-lo (emprant <link linkend=\"run-"
"execute\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Executa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Executa</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice></link>) per a veure el resultat. En els exemples "
"següents s'espera que coneixereu l'exercici."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might have noticed that this second example uses a lot more code. You "
"have also seen a couple of new commands. Here a short explanation of all the "
"new commands:"
msgstr ""
"Podeu haver notat que aquest segon exemple utilitza molt més codi. També "
"s'han fet servir un parell d'ordres noves. Aquí teniu una breu explicació de "
"totes les ordres noves:"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After a <userinput>reset</userinput> command everything is like is was when "
"you had just started &kturtle;."
msgstr ""
"Després d'una ordre <userinput>reset</userinput> tot queda com estava quan "
"vau iniciar el &kturtle;."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>canvassize 200,200</userinput> sets the canvas width and height "
"to 200 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm>. The width and the "
"height are equal, so the canvas will be a square."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>canvassize 200,200</userinput> estableix amplada i alçada del "
"llenç a 200 x 200 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">píxels</glossterm>. "
"L'amplada és igual que l'alçada, per tant, el llenç serà quadrat."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>canvascolor 0,0,0</userinput> makes the canvas black. "
"<userinput>0,0,0</userinput> is a <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-"
"combination</glossterm> where all values are set to <userinput>0</"
"userinput>, which results in black."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>canvascolor 0,0,0</userinput> fa que el llenç sigui negre. "
"<userinput>0,0,0</userinput> és una <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">combinació "
"RGB</glossterm> on tots els valors estan establerts a <userinput>0</"
"userinput>, el qual resultarà en el color negre."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>pencolor 255,0,0</userinput> sets the color of the pen to red. "
"<userinput>255,0,0</userinput> is a <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-"
"combination</glossterm> where only the red value is set to <userinput>255</"
"userinput> (fully on) while the others (green and blue) are set to "
"<userinput>0</userinput> (fully off). This results in a bright shade of red."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>pencolor 255,0,0</userinput> estableix el color del dibuix a "
"vermell. <userinput>255,0,0</userinput> és una <glossterm linkend=\"rgb"
"\">combinació RGB</glossterm> on només el valor vermell està establert a "
"<userinput>255</userinput> (completament) on tots els altres valors (verd i "
"blau) estan establerts a <userinput>0</userinput> (no gens). Això resultarà "
"en un to més brillant de color vermell."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not understand the color values, be sure to read the glossary on "
"<glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-combination</glossterm>."
msgstr ""
"Si no enteneu els valors de color, assegureu-vos de llegir el glossari sobre "
"la <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">combinació RGB </glossterm>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>penwidth 5</userinput> sets the width (the size) of the pen to "
"<userinput>5</userinput> <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm>. "
"From now on every line the turtle draw will have a thickness of "
"<userinput>5</userinput>, until we change the <userinput>penwidth</"
"userinput> to something else."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>penwidth 5</userinput> canvia l'amplada (la mida) del traç a "
"<userinput>5</userinput> <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">píxels</glossterm>. A "
"partir d'aquest moment, cada línia que dibuixi la tortuga ho farà amb "
"<userinput>5</userinput> píxels d'amplada, fins que canvieu el valor de "
"l'amplada de <userinput>penwidth</userinput> a una altra cosa."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>go 20,20</userinput> commands the turtle to go to a certain place "
"on the canvas. Counted from the upper left corner, this place is 20 "
"<glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm> across from the left, and "
"20 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm> down from the top of the "
"canvas. Note that using the <userinput>go</userinput> command the turtle "
"will not draw a line."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>go 20,20</userinput> permet a la tortuga anar a un cert lloc "
"sobre el llenç. Comptat a partir de la cantonada superior esquerra, aquest "
"lloc és de 20 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">píxels</glossterm> cap a "
"l'esquerra, i 20 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">píxels</glossterm> cap avall "
"des de la part superior del llenç. Nota: Quan empreu l'ordre <userinput>go</"
"userinput> no us dibuixarà una línia."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>direction 135</userinput> set the turtle's direction. The "
"<userinput>turnleft</userinput> and <userinput>turnright</userinput> "
"commands change the turtle's angle starting from its current direction. The "
"<userinput>direction</userinput> command changes the turtle's angle from "
"zero, and thus is not relative to the turtle previous direction."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>direction 135</userinput> estableix la direcció de la tortuga. "
"Les ordres <userinput>turnleft</userinput> i <userinput>turnright</"
"userinput> canvien d'angle la tortuga a partir de la seva direcció actual. "
"L'ordre <userinput>direction</userinput> canvia d'angle la tortuga des de "
"zero, i per tant no és relativa a l'anterior direcció de la tortuga."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the <userinput>direction</userinput> command a lot of "
"<userinput>forward</userinput> and <userinput>turnleft</userinput> commands "
"follow. These command do the actual drawing."
msgstr ""
"Després de l'ordre <userinput>direction</userinput> segueixen una gran "
"quantitat d'ordres <userinput>forward</userinput> i <userinput>turnleft</"
"userinput>. Aquestes ordres fan el dibuix."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At last another <userinput>go</userinput> command is used to move the turtle "
"aside."
msgstr ""
"Al final una altra ordre <userinput>go</userinput> s'utilitza per a moure la "
"tortuga a un costat."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure you follow the links to the reference. The reference explains each "
"command more thoroughly."
msgstr ""
"Assegureu-vos d'emprar els enllaços a la referència. La referència explica "
"cadascuna de les ordres amb més detall."
